OL,3,C'Lost for words at the kindness of
OL,4,Cpeople' bereaved Dad leads charity walk
OL,6,FA retired teacher from Liverpool has
OL,7,Fled a charity walk in memory of his
OL,8,Fdaughter, who passed away 28 years ago
OL,9,Fwhen she was just 13 years old.
OL,11,FGed Finnegan's annual "Kate's Coastal
OL,12,FWalk" set off from Otterspool,
OL,13,FLiverpool with more than a hundred
OL,14,Fpeople taking on the marathon-distance
OL,15,Froute to Leasowe Lighthouse, Wirral,
OL,16,Fcrossing the Mersey by ferry.
