OL,3,C'Lost for words at the kindness of
OL,4,Cpeople' bereaved Dad leads charity walk
OL,6,FIt is the eighth year Ged has led the
OL,7,Fcharity coastal walk and has helped to
OL,8,Fraise about #130,000 for Zoe's Place,
OL,9,Fthe children's hospice now known as
OL,10,F"Little Lights'.
OL,12,FGed said: "It means everything to me
OL,13,Fand it's hard to put it into words.
OL,15,F"No-one's ever met my daughter, aside
OL,16,Ffrom my son who's here, so I just
OL,17,Fthink what are you doing here and
OL,18,Fwalking 26 miles, they are here at
OL,19,F7:30am and they won't get home until
OL,20,Fabout 6:30pm carrying the buckets and
OL,21,Fit is just remarkable."
