OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774865180
OL,3,C'Lost for words at the kindness of
OL,4,Cpeople' bereaved Dad leads charity walk
OL,6,FIt is all in memory of Ged's daughter
OL,7,FKate who died at the age of 13 in
OL,8,F1998. She had a sudden heart attack in
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FGed Finnegan's daughter Kate died in
OL,12,F1998 at the age of 13, he says the
OL,13,Fannual charity walk helps to keep her
OL,14,Fmemory alive.
OL,16,FGed said the annual walk is always
OL,17,Fvery emotional for him and his family.
